commentPostTextItems.html: Convincing win for the Windies with Gayle and Chattergoon coming up with an unbroken partnership of 156 runs for the opening wicket. West Indies have won the series with 2 more matches to be played at Trinidad. Gayle adjudged Man-of-Match for his all-round performance. Please join us for the next match to be played on Saturday. Cheers and bye!
